Package: wyz.code.offensiveProgramming
Type: Package
Title: Wyzardry Code Offensive Programming
Version: 1.01.001
Author: Fabien GELINEAU <neonira@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Fabien GELINEAU <neonira@gmail.com>
Description: Allows to change R coding from defensive programming to offensive
    programming. Provides code instrumentation to ease this change. Should reduce
    the code size as many controls and type checks have no more reason to exist.
